#                                                                              #
# Variable Name: gap_lock_exceptions                                           #
# Scope: GLOBAL                                                                #
# Access Type: Dynamic                                                         #
# Data Type: Filename                                                          #
# Default Value: ""                                                            #
# Valid Values:                                                                #
#                                                                              #
#                                                                              #
# Creation Date: 2016-04-18                                                    #
#                                                                              #
# Description: Test Cases of Dynamic System Variable "gap_lock_exceptions"     #
#              that checks behavior of this variable in the following ways     #
#              * Default Value                                                 #
#              * Valid & Invalid values                                        #
#              * Scope & Access method                                         #
#              * Data Integrity                                                #
#                                                                              #
# Reference:                                                                   #
